data.meta_description: Your life is the best story! Just start your blog today!
data.text:
[Note (18 Feb. 2015): After I helped expand Miss Darcey-Alden's Harry Potter Wiki page (which some of it was adapted from her real-world Wikipedia page available under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike License), I decided to start this...]

Miss Ellie D Alden

Facebook | Tumblr | About | Gallery

Welcome to Miss Ellie D Alden, an unofficial fansite/page dedicated to 19-year-old English actress Ellie Darcey-Alden, who is probably most recognisable as young Lily Evans Potter in Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 2 and Francesca Latimer in the Doctor Who Series 7 Christmas special, "The Snowmen."

Here, you will find the latest news, photos, and more!

As of 18 Feb. 2015, this page is currently a work-in-progress, so please be patient as content is still being added.

Thank you for stopping by!

reblog
